id: pm-7jkm
title: Fix parser overrides for core commands without positional args
description: Parser overrides registered by extensions were not applied to core commands like list when invoked without positional args.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[3]: "area:agent-ux","area:extensions","audit:2026-04-25"
created_at: "2026-04-25T20:01:14.954Z"
updated_at: "2026-04-25T20:03:57.393Z"
deadline: "2026-04-27T20:01:14.954Z"
author: codex-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: Core parser overrides affect built-in commands with and without positional args; regression test covers pm list override.
parent: pm-o7be
reporter: codex-agent
severity: high
environment: cli
repro_steps: "Install parser extension overriding list limit, run pm list --json."
resolution: Patched wrapped action forwarding to replay parser-mutated args via Commander processedArgs and synced option values before invoking core handlers.
expected_result: filters.limit reflects override and result count is constrained.
actual_result: override ignored for core list command.
component: extension-runtime
regression: true
customer_impact: Agent-authored parser extensions cannot reliably shape built-in command UX.
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T20:01:14.954Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm context --limit 10; pm search 'parser override core command' --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 20; pm list-in-progress --limit 20. Net-new because no active item tracked no-positional core parser forwarding bug."
  "2026-04-25T20:03:44.443Z",codex-agent,"Implemented core parser-forwarding fix in wrapped action dispatch by replaying parser-mutated args through Commander processedArgs and syncing option values via setOptionValueWithSource. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts (61 passed)."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T20:01:14.954Z",codex-agent,Failure reproduced in /tmp dogfood project via local extension parser override.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T20:01:14.954Z",codex-agent,Wrapper-level action interception must preserve Commander processedArgs semantics for variadic/single-arg commands.
