close_reason: Parser overrides now apply to core commands without positional args; integration regression test passes.
body: "Dogfood evidence: extension registerParser('list') injected limit=1 but pm list --json kept filters.limit=null and returned full counts. Root cause in wrapped action forwarding only patched user options objects, not Commander processed args/options pipeline for core commands."
